import React from 'react'
import Container from 're'

function Footer() {
  return (
    <footer>
      <Container>
        <Row>
          <Col xs={12} md={8}>
            xs=12 md=8
          </Col>
          <Col xs={6} md={4}>
            xs=6 md=4
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </footer>
  )
}

export default Footer
